Method Detail

getGroupAddress

public final byte[] getGroupAddress()
A field whose interpretation depends on message type. Typically this field identifies an IPv6 multicast group address. The Group Address field is set to zero when sending a General Query, and set to the IP multicast address being queried when sending a Group-Specific Query or Group-and-Source-Specific Query.
